snippet.title: Friday Night Funkin' VS Huggy Wuggy Week (FNF Mod/Hard/DEMO) (Poppy Playtime/Horror Mod)
snippet.description:
Friday Night Funkin' VS Huggy Wuggy (FULL WEEK/DEMO) for the PC in 2160p Ultra HD, but this time we battle Huggy Wuggy from Huggy Wuggy Poppy Playtime Horror Game. 

Just in time for Halloween! Huggy Wuggy is a secondary antagonist in the 2021 horror game Poppy Playtime, serving as the main antagonist of "A Tight Squeeze", the first chapter of the game. Huggy Wuggy was created by Playtime CO. The toy soon became the most successful product of the company. But he was eventually modified at some point prior to the events of the game with a transferred but corrupted human conscience to which they turned him into a monster. 

I have seen Markiplier play this the other day and I have been waiting for Poppy Playtime Chapter 2 to be released, but at least we got a poppy playtime in fnf now. Will Boyfriend and Girlfriend defeat Huggy Wuggy or will bf and gf lose to him?

Game Note by Dev: Sing against Huggy Wuggy from Poppy Playtime! I made this mod because I really enjoy the game and really like the character. Hope you enjoy it! Poppy Playtime by MOB Games, Psych Engine by ShadowMario, Art, Music, and some Programming by KJ Elliott.

KJ Elliott - Creator of the FNF Vs Poppy Playtime mod:
https://twitter.com/KjEll1ott

FNF Vs Huggy Wuggy Poppy Playtime Download:
https://gamejolt.com/games/huggywuggyfnf/657741

► Disclaimer: This video is intended for viewers aged 13+ and older.
